@page "ESG"
@model BA.KonnexResources.Pages.ESGModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "ESG";
}
<div class="container-fluid home-wrapper pb-100">
    <div class="container custom-container">
        <div class="row flex-center calc-right">
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <h1 class="mb-0" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Lenie Wilkie</h1>
                <h2 class="mb-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">ESG Coordinator, Mackay resident</h2>
                <p class="text-md mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">“A responsible mining operation has
                    the potential to bring sustainable economic benefits to Mackay. I would love to see local businesses
                    thriving and my kids and their classmates with more opportunities to make high-paying wages in town.
                    I’ve found the leadership at Konnex Resources to be great partners for creating these opportunities
                    while placing the highest importance on protecting the area’s lands, waters, and wildlife.”</p>
                <a class="red-btn" href="#" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Have your say</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7 p-0">
                <img class="img-fluid w-100" src="/images/lenie-wilkie.jpeg" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid pt-80">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 pb-100">
                @* <h3 class="head-sm" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Focused on working with regulators,
                    consultants, and the people of Central Idaho to responsibly advance the Empire Mine Project. </h3> *@
                <p class="text-lg pl-60 text-darkblue" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
                    We are committed to being a leader in modern mining practices by making environmental stewardship,
                    social responsibility, and transparent governance (ESG) the foundation of everything we do. In June
                    2021, we established our ESG & Sustainability Committee. The role of the committee is to ensure the
                    practices of Konnex Resources and its parent company, Phoenix Copper Limited, are meeting and
                    exceeding the laws and regulations put in place to protect the natural resources and communities
                    located in and around its mining operations.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid py-100 pr team-container mt-60">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row flex-center calc-left">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <img data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000" class="img-fluid w-100" src="/images/esg.jpeg" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 px-50">
                <h3 class="head-lg text-white" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Environmental Stewardship
                </h3>
                <p class="text-white text-md mt-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Custer County and Lost
                    River Valley residents have a fierce pride in the outstanding beauty of their surroundings. As the
                    Empire Mine and other exploration projects advance in the area, the Konnex team continues to make
                    environmental stewardship our top priority.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12 pb-100">
    <p class="text-lg py-4 pl-70 text-darkblue" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">In 2017,
        <strong>Konnex</strong> hired an independent environmental engineering company to conduct baseline studies.
        Since then, the company has tracked and studied a variety of elements of the environment including climate and
        air quality, surface and groundwater hydrology, soil characterization, transportation, water use and treatment,
        plant and wildlife, community and infrastructure planning, and much more. This data has helped Konnex understand
        the existing environmental conditions before the start of mining activities and will continue serving as a guide
        for Konnex’s development plans. It will also serve as a benchmark for reclamation at the end of the mine life.
    </p>
</div>
<div width="100%" class="container-fluid" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
    <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 mx-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Empire Mine Environmental Information –
            information
            based on baseline and socio-economic studies by an independent environmental engineering firm.</h2>
        @* <img class="mb-5" src=" /images/chart1cropped.jpeg" width='100%' data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000"
            /> *@
    </div>
