        <ul class="text-lg py-4 pl-70 pr-60 text-darkblue" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
        <li><strong>Wildlife & Vegetation:</strong> Our activities are not damaging to local wildlife or plant life
        and will not affect the biodiversity of the area.</li>
        <li><strong>Water:</strong> The mine is a zero-discharge facility meaning water runoff and pollution is not
        a concern. All water will evaporate or be absorbed into the ground. The mines are dry and situated 900
