        </div>
        <div class="card card-noise">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center" data-bs-toggle='modal'
                data-bs-target="#noise-card">
                <img src='/images/noise-nobg.png' width='160px' />
                <h5 class="card-title text-center mt-3">Pollution</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Regulators have strict rules around noise, light and dust pollution. Konnex will be
                    required to prove it will eliminate any impact of the pollutants.</p>
