</div>
<div class='mt-5' width='100%' display='flex' align='center'>
    <h2 class="mb-3 mx-5 ms-50" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Visual Expectations</h2>
    <p class='text-lg mx-5' data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Expected view of Empire Mine site from three
        different
        perspectives show very little visual impact as a
        result of
        mine activities. </p>
</div>
